  "“I’m so sorry, Nina,” I say.",
  "“If there’s anything I can do…”",
  "",
  "Nina’s eyes lower onto the disaster on the kitchen floor.",
  "“You can clean up this disgusting mess you left in my kitchen while I fix this problem.”",
  "",
