  "It’s not like they’re saying she plotted to kill her daughter.",
  "If that were true, she would be in prison right now.",
  "Forever.",
  "",
  "Still.",
  "As much as I worried about Nina’s mental status, I never truly believed she had the capacity for real violence.",
  "She’s capable of much more than I thought.",
  "",
  "For the first time since Enzo rejected me, I think back to the panic in his eyes as he hurried toward the front door.",
