  "",
  "“Nina!”",
  "Stewart cries.",
  "“Get yourself cleaned up!”",
  "",
  "“Right,” I say quickly.",
  "“I… I’m so sorry.",
  "I…”",
  "",
  "I drop the papers on Stewart’s desk and hurry out of the office as fast as I can.",
  "I grab my coat to hide my blouse, all the while blinking back tears.",
